title: Ars Amandi - Art of Love 1983 - ITA-ENG
description:
TITLE: Ars Amandi
AKA: Ars Amandi - L'arte di amare - Art of Love
YEAR: 1983

The setting is Rome, 8 A.D., where the poet Ovid watches over an epoch of forbidden seduction and unnatural acts among maidens, centurions, servant girls and the occasional farm animal. Marina Pierro , Michele Placido, Laura Betti, Milena Vukotic and Massimo Girotti star in this sumptuous art/smut classic.
